1
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:05,400
This is Ms. Jeans.

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:07,400
The one who designed Yuka.

3
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:10,400
I want our game’s main character

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,240
to be an ordinary guy

5
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:14,800
that anyone could fall in love with.

6
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:18,000
My boss gave me the task of

7
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,880
winning your heart.

8
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:19,920
Hey, you!

9
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:21,600
Don’t waste your time.

10
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:27,280
I think Hill's really sincere.

11
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:29,800
Don’t you agree?

12
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:46,400
(Are you sure he'll arrive early?)

13
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,440
(He'll be there.)

14
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,280
[yawning sticker]

15
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:55,720
(Don't break your promise.)

16
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:58,880
(You too. Tell Hill about that.)

17
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,000
[sticker]

18
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,120
[sticker]

19
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,800
About the other day…

20
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:10,400
I'm sorry. I got carried away.

21
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,960
That's not right.

22
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,440
I'm really sorry.

23
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,800
I just got carried away.

24
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:19,000
Please forgive me. I'm so sorry.

25
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:21,200
Is that…

26
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,760
Is that enough?

27
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:24,800
No!

28
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,600
Hey, you!

29
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:26,800
Hey, are you alright?

30
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,400
Just stay still.

31
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,400
I'll take care of it.

32
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,200
Okay?

33
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,000
Be still.

34
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,600
Trust me, okay?

35
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,000
Keep still.

36
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,360
Keep still.

37
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,280
Is it gone yet?

38
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,800
Yeah, it's gone now.

39
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,600
You sure?

40
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,800
Yeah, just take a look.

41
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,680
Thank you.

42
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,200
Anyway,

43
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,400
what are you doing here?

44
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,200
Well,

45
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,640
About what I did the other day, I'm—

46
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,520
That's enough.

47
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,680
You should go.

48
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,800
Thank you for helping just now.

49
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:34,760
What?

50
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,280
That’s it?

51
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,040
Yes.

52
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,520
Anything else?

53
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,680
I said thank you, didn't I?

54
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,800
But I helped you get rid of the lizard.

55
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,880
Cheers. Much obliged. Thank you very much!

56
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,600
You can go now.

57
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,880
I've got work to do.

58
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,920
I won't give up.

59
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,000
Stop grinning

60
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,400
Stop grinning

61
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,520
and go back to work.

62
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,960
Bay.

63
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,600
What?

64
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,800
Are you okay?

65
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,400
You look so serious.

66
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,960
Girl problems?

67
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,800
It's worse than that.

68
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,560
He's got such a big ego, I swear.

69
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,240
I see.

70
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:04,720
So you still haven’t made
any progress with Mr. Phat?

71
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,120
Don't rub it in.

72
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,000
I'm already hurt.

73
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,080
Shouldn’t have kissed him.

74
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,920
You kind of deserved it.

75
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,400
You went overboard.

76
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,320
Whose side are you on?

77
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,640
Yours.

78
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,880
You rarely mess up,
so I had to tease you a bit.

79
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,760
You little…

80
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:29,400
Still can’t believe that a player like you

81
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,080
is getting his claws clipped by Mr. Phat.

82
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,840
Come on.

83
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:37,080
I heard your mission

84
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,200
to hold hands with Boss

85
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,720
failed miserably too.

86
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,400
It totally did.

87
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,760
It’s harder than I thought.

88
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,200
Indeed.

89
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,000
What if…

90
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,600
I'm not cut out for this?

91
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,000
Jeez, don’t get all dramatic now.

92
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,800
Jeez, don’t get all dramatic now.

93
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,520
Alright.

94
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,480
I'll tell you Yuka-chan's secret.

95
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,200
How's that?

96
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,160
What secret?

97
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:20,560
Yuka-chan is modeled after Jeans.

98
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,280
So don’t give up, dude.

99
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,000
This job brings you closer to Yuka-chan

100
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,400
without you realizing it.

101
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,560
See?

102
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,120
Cool secret, right?

103
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,120
Hello, Hill.

104
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,600
There you are!

105
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,520
Took me forever.

106
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:19,680
Oh.

107
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,600
Me?

108
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,600
Is there something you need?

109
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,280
Yu—

110
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,800
Ms. Jeans.

111
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,600
Actually,

112
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,360
I just finished designing
a new outfit for Yuka.

113
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,800
So I'd like you to take some photos for me.

114
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,080
But…

115
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:42,760
The game’s no longer being updated.

116
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:48,600
I made it for the day when
"Yuka! Love Me Please" returns.

117
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,760
So there won't be any gaps.

118
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,560
Can you help me out?

119
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,400
That would be my pleasure!

120
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,160
How about getting something done first?

121
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,760
Seriously?

122
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,600
I'm just borrowing him for a bit.

123
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,680
Are you feeling…

124
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:14,680
Jealous?

125
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,200
Protective.

126
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:18,000
I worry he won't finish his main tasks.

127
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:22,680
Then I’ll come along
and see how it turns out.

128
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,880
Really?

129
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,120
That's great.

130
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,800
I guess

131
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,800
having you here

132
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,680
would be fun for me.

133
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,280
Thanks, dude.

134
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,360
Looks like the new guy

135
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,600
is really obedient.

136
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,080
Hey.

137
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,280
Hey.

138
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,040
Hill!

139
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,680
You still alive, Hill?

140
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,040
Hill?

141
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,280
Yeah?

142
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:11,880
Hill!

143
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,400
Well? How is it?

144
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,400
Do I look cute in the photos?

145
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,120
Show me!

146
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,320
They're all blurry, Ms. Jeans.

147
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,400
What the heck?

148
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,000
Can't take proper photos?

149
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,000
Hey.

150
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,400
Hey.

151
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:02,480
You're lucky you got some shots.

152
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,600
I was joking.

153
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:10,400
Help me out. How should Yuka pose when

154
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,480
she's wearing this outfit?

155
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,680
Well,

156
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,720
Let's see…

157
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,400
How about her signature pose?

158
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:23,760
I bet the fans would love that.

159
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:26,800
It’s been a while since
the game had an update.

160
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,080
Perfect!

161
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,400
You know,

162
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:38,600
you’re the perfect man for this job.

163
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:41,600
You know Yuka better than anyone.

164
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,720
I wouldn’t go that far.

165
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,280
Damn.

166
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,920
He's so stiff.

167
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,760
What’s stiff?

168
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,600
The zipper.

169
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:02,200
Wow,

170
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,800
It's so stiff!

171
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,160
It's really stiff.

172
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,200
Can you zip it up for me?

173
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,000
Help me out, Hill.

174
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,960
Sorry.

175
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,000
It’s…

176
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,200
Come on, hurry.

177
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:26,280
Excuse me.

178
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:26,960
Yeah.

179
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:29,760
Go ahead.

180
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,560
The zipper seems fine.

181
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,800
Not stiff at all.

182
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,440
I mean,

183
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,000
I’m a woman, after all.

184
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,400
How could I be stronger than you?

185
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,880
You're a woman.

186
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,880
So be more careful.

187
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,360
Are you being protective?

188
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,360
Or you're…

189
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,000
possessive of me?

190
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,160
That's enough.

191
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:15,480
Once we're done with this pose today,

192
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,200
let’s have lunch together.

193
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,400
My treat.

194
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:19,920
No need.

195
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,840
I need Hill to take care of an urgent task.

196
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,720
Next time, then.

197
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,960
We’ll continue the shoot at my studio.

198
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,400
After hours, to avoid problems.

199
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,320
Sure.

200
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,200
Hey, Boss?

201
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,000
What’s this urgent task

202
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,200
you need me to do?

203
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,560
So,

204
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:52,360
this is the urgent task?

205
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,400
Ramen with soft-boiled egg is the best.

206
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:57,600
But I can't make soft-boiled eggs.

207
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,360
Really, Boss?

208
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,000
You could've just told Auntie Un, the maid.

209
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,360
You could've just told Auntie Un, the maid.

210
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:03,280
She’s a better cook than I am.

211
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:07,360
It’s lunch break.
I didn’t want to bother her.

212
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:09,600
So you came to me.

213
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,520
I’ll do it myself.

214
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,840
Just kidding, Boss.

215
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,800
Of course I’ll do it for you.

216
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,560
Easy.

217
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,280
Mission Two

218
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,520
is to hold hands

219
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,400
with Boss.

220
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,200
Let me help.

221
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,600
Looks like you're struggling.

222
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,520
I’ll handle it.

223
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:52,920
I’ll peel the egg myself.

224
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,200
But it’s still—

225
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:55,960
Hot !

226
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,400
Boss!

227
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,080
Boss!

228
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,720
Don't.

229
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,000
Are you okay?

230
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,400
Are you okay?

231
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,360
I’m fine. Just a little burn.

232
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:03,920
That won't do.

233
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,160
Just a second.

234
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,000
Ouch.

235
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,960
Here you go, Boss.

236
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,560
Give me your hand. Trust me.

237
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,080
Boss.

238
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:08,280
Mind if I borrow him to help out
at the studio fort the day?

239
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:09,800
Not a chance.

240
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:13,360
There's work I need him to help with today.

241
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,800
Oh, is that so?

242
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:17,920
I see.

243
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,000
That's okay.

244
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,280
Your hand, Boss?

245
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,200
Here you go.

246
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,560
Enjoy your meal.

247
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,800
I’ll head back to the kitchen.

248
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,200
We're super busy right now.

249
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:47,920
Wait.

250
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,600
I have some updates.

251
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,680
Can the gossip wait until later?

252
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:52,680
I’m busy right now.

253
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:56,720
Junji’s about to fall in love again.

254
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,000
With who?

255
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,080
I thought you were busy?

256
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,280
We have enough chefs.

257
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,360
Let them handle it.

258
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,720
I’d just be in the way.

259
00:16:08,160 --> 00:16:10,400
So you make time when it's gossip, huh?

260
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:13,520
So, who’s Junji falling for?

261
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,320
Hill.

262
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,200
Junji likes Hill.

263
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:20,360
I'm sure of it.

264
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:22,480
The new guy who's always with him?

265
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:25,000
Of course.

266
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,040
He picked Junji as the reference material

267
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:29,520
and took on the task of flirting with him.

268
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,360
They're always together.

269
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:32,640
Right?

270
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:34,160
You agree with me, right?

271
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:36,080
Didn’t you just say you're sure of it?

272
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,800
Around ninety percent.

273
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,360
In that case...

274
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:41,760
For this wedding,

275
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:44,280
let me be in charge of catering.

276
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:46,320
I’ll give it my all.

277
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,200
I'll go all out with gourmet Thai food.

278
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,920
Then I’ll be the organizer!

279
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:53,400
I’ll put my all into

280
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,440
the themes, costumes, hair and makeup.

281
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:57,920
Make it grand and glorious for Junji!

282
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,800
One-two, one-two-three. One-two-victory!

283
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:02,160
Isn't that the cheerleading thing?

284
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:07,800
If we hold the wedding in Thailand,

285
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:10,120
do we have to do one in Japan too?

286
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:11,040
Of course!

287
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:12,200
It's a matter of respect.

288
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:19,600
(Did you forget?)

289
00:17:19,600 --> 00:17:22,040
(You said you'd help me out!)

290
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:28,000
(I didn't! I'll be the peacemaker.)

291
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,800
(Relax, okay?)

292
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:31,520
[sticker]

